Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Cricket Equipment Market

The cricket equipment market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 5.0% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028 and is estimated to reach USD 17 million by 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on cricket equipment market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth. The rise in the comfort of the customers is escalating the growth of cricket equipment market.

The cricket equipment comprises of ball, bat, batting gloves, abdominal guard, wicket keeping gloves, thigh guard, forearm guard, shin pads, leg pads, stump and bails, and so forth. The equipment is being created and produced according to the consumers. Various raw materials are being utilized for each product and the size of the equipment

Major factors that are expected to boost the growth of the cricket equipment market in the forecast period are the development in the production procedure. Furthermore, the accessibility of several raw material is further anticipated to propel the growth of the cricket equipment market. Moreover, the consciousness regarding the trends is further estimated to cushion the growth of the cricket equipment market. On the other hand, the shutdown of the production of the raw material such as wood, leather, and other for the manufacturing of the equipment is further projected to impede the growth of the shutdown of many manufacturing in the timeline period.

In addition, the rise in the disposable income, luxurious lifestyles, the popularity of the sports events, celebrity endorsements will further provide potential opportunities for the growth of the cricket equipment market in the coming years. However, the government has postponed and cancelled cricket events which might further challenge the growth of the cricket equipment market in the near future.

